## TRANSIÇÕES DE TELA

### Stack Navigation (Forward / Push):
```
Tela A → Tela B
[Tela A slide out left] + [Tela B slide in from right]
```
- Tipo: SLIDE_IN, direction: LEFT
- Duração: 300-350ms
- Easing: gentle ou ease-in-out

### Stack Navigation (Back / Pop):
```
Tela B → Tela A
[Tela B slide out right] + [Tela A slide in from left]
```
- Tipo: SLIDE_OUT, direction: RIGHT
- Duração: 300-350ms
- Easing: gentle ou ease-in-out

### Modal (Open):
```
[Overlay fade in] + [Sheet slide up from bottom]
```
- Tipo: SLIDE_IN, direction: BOTTOM
- Duração: 350-400ms
- Easing: ease-out ou gentle

### Modal (Close):
```
[Sheet slide down] + [Overlay fade out]
```
- Tipo: SLIDE_OUT, direction: BOTTOM
- Duração: 250-300ms
- Easing: ease-in

### Tab Switch:
```
[Tab A fade out] + [Tab B fade in]
```
- Tipo: DISSOLVE ou SMART_ANIMATE
- Duração: 200-250ms
- Easing: ease-in-out

